name: 【Art Style】ERO404 Style
description:
Introduction

A LoRA model trained with illustrations and comic images created by ERO404. The trigger tag is 'ero404'. 0.6 ~ 0.8 weights are good. Due to comic images containing speech bubbles that can affect the generated results and are hard to losslessly remove. Therefore, pls try to add '(speech bubble:1.2)' in negative prompt to prevent this bad effect. The preview images are generated using 1.6 version (original) YesMix.

Cautions (Must Read)

For anime model,

pls disable 'face restoration' during generating.

pls disable 'face restoration' during generating.

pls disable 'face restoration' during generating.

  • Some preview images are generated using 'Hires Fix' and upscaled using 'SD Upscale'. Thus, if you wanna generate the preview images, pls download the original preview images and analyze them using 'PNG INFO' in webui to get all generating information.

  • The maximum of generating resolution should not exceed 1024 theoretically, otherwise extra/deformed head/limbs will be waiting for you :). Try to use 'hires fix' to prevent this problem and help to generate higher-resolution images.

  • For 784mb VAEs (NovelAI, Anythingv3, Orangemix, Counterfeit) users, make sure add '--no-half-vae' in command line of webui to prevent generating black images. See voldy's log for the details of edit method. For high-performance GPU, make sure 'medvram' and 'lowvram' mode are disabled.
